Package com.example.vibeverse

Class Photograph

java.lang.Object
com.example.vibeverse.Photograph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Photograph extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a photograph associated with a mood event.

This class stores information about an image including its URI, file size (in kilobytes), an optional bitmap, the date the image was taken, and an optional location. It implements Serializable so that instances can be passed between activities via Intents.
